</li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFPrentiss2003" class="citation book cs1">Prentiss, Craig R. (2003). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=A6PtfoiPlX0C&amp;pg=PA132">"<span class="cs1-kern-left"></span>"Loathsome unto Thy People": The Latter-day Saints and Racial Categorization"</a>. <i>Religion and the Creation of Race and Ethnicity: An Introduction</i>. NYU Press. p.&#160;132. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-8147-6882-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8147-6882-2"><bdi>978-0-8147-6882-2</bdi></a>. <q>Mormons were accused by their persecutors in Missouri of being abolitionists and trying to promote slave rebellions</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=%22Loathsome+unto+Thy+People%22%3A+The+Latter-day+Saints+and+Racial+Categorization&amp;rft.btitle=Religion+and+the+Creation+of+Race+and+Ethnicity%3A+An+Introduction&amp;rft.pages=132&amp;rft.pub=NYU+Press&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8147-6882-2&amp;rft.aulast=Prentiss&amp;rft.aufirst=Craig+R.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DA6PtfoiPlX0C%26pg%3DPA132&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span style="white-space: nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot" title="Wikipedia:Link rot"><span title="&#160;Dead link tagged December 2023">permanent dead link</span></a></i>&#93;</span></sup></span>
</li>
